---
import MainLayout from "../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
import "../styles/FAQ.css";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
import Navbar from "../components/Navbar.astro";
---

<MainLayout title="FAQ">
  <Navbar />
  <article>
    <p class="Questions">Q1: How do we submit our hours?</p>
    <p class="Answers">
      A1: There is an hour submission form that is available in the hour
      submission tab on the top right.
    </p>
    <br />
    <p class="Questions">
      Q2: Is there a way for checking the progress made on our hours?
    </p>
    <p class="Answers">
      A2: Yes, that can be done through the search button present in the hours
      submission tab.
    </p>
    <br />
    <p class="Questions">Q3:Are there website sync dates?</p>
    <p class="Answers">
      A3:There are no more website sync dates as the system automatically
      updates, however the submission forms will be closed for verification
      days.
    </p>
    <br />
    <p class="Questions">Q4: Is it required to attend all the meetings?</p>
    <p class="Answers">
      A4: Yes, it is required to attend all the meetings per semester.
    </p>
    <br />
    <p class="Questions">
      Q5: Do you need to resubmit your hours if you put in the wrong
      information?
    </p>
    <p class="Answers">A5: Yes.</p>
    <br />
    <p class="Questions">
      Q6: Who should be the only one to contact the officers?
    </p>
    <p class="Answers">A6: YOU!!</p>
    <!--<br>
    <p class="Questions">Q7: If I submitted a club collaboration form, when do I get back to hear back?</p>
    <p class="Answers">A7: In 2 weeks.</p>-->
    <br />
    <p class="Questions">Q7: What if I did not get a picture for the event?</p>
    <p class="Answers">
      A7: If you volunteer at a recurring event, you can submit a picture of a
      sign up sheet for the first time you volunteer for that event. The rest of
      the submissions from that opportunity MUST have picture proof with you in
      it.
    </p>
  </article>
</MainLayout>
